            <h4>Trial fitting</h4>
            <p>We select the appropriate trial lens and evaluate the fit, corneal clearance, and visual acuity achieved. Adjustments are made until the optimal diagnostic lens is found.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="paso">
          <div class="paso-num">3</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Custom lens order</h4>
            <p>We order your lens with the exact parameters measured in consultation. Manufacturing takes 1–2 weeks. Every lens is custom-made to your unique corneal topography.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="paso">
          <div class="paso-num">4</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Training & follow-up</h4>
            <p>We teach you the correct insertion and removal technique, care routine, and saline solution filling. Follow-up visits at 2 and 4 weeks optimize your adaptation and final vision.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

